<h2>Methodology: How We Evaluated These Coverage Options</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Choosing the best travel insurance companies requires more than comparing prices. A cheap policy may provide limited protection when travelers need help most. VentureBurn evaluated providers using the following criteria:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Coverage Breadth: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">We picked companies that offer strong protection users. We looked out for coverages like trip cancellation, trip interruption, medical emergencies, emergency evacuation, travel delays, baggage loss and missed connections.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Medical Benefits: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">Medical emergencies in countries overseas can be very costly. Medical coverage limits, evacuation benefits and access to emergency assistance services were discussed.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Customer Experience: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">We took into account how easy it is to buy policies, access mobile tools, claim information and customer support availability.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Flexibility: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">higher ratings were given to providers that provided options for customized plans, optional upgrades, and CFAR coverage.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Value for Money: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">The provider that is usually the cheapest is not always the best. We searched for companies that were providing solid benefits vs. costs.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Specialized Travel Needs:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Some providers excel in specific categories, including adventure travel, cruises, annual travel, </span><a href="https://www.lcsliving.com/resources/for-seniors/senior-lifestyle/7-senior-travel-tips-what-to-consider-when-planning-a-trip/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400;">senior travelers</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, family vacations and international medical protection.</span></li>
</ul>
